Letter in page 24: 
"Thanks for letting me stay the night! I just wanted to let you know that, even though my income yesterday was 0, it didn't affect me at all. 
You know...
When I was singing, you went to the crowd and yelled. 'Whoever this girl is, she'll definitely get famous in the future! And I promise to help her achieve her dreams!'
That made me feel suuuuuuper ashamed, but inside you made me feel so happy. If I'd stay more time with you, I'd definitely fall in love with you. So I'll try my best to achieve the dreams you support me with so much!

I'll definitely make it, so you better keep cheering me on! 

Love, An. I'll leave with you my most prized possesion." 
Translation is a bit rough, but this is as best as I can. Hope it gets the idea across.
